spec_data.Name: golang-googlecode-sqlite-devel
spec_data.Description:
Trivial sqlite3 binding for Go

This package has no exported API. It registers a driver for the standard Go
database/SQL package.

This package contains library source intended for
building other packages which use import path with
code.google.com/p/gosqlite prefix.
